{"word":"Image","slug":"image","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Image</b> For idols<br/> <a href='S:Idolatry'>Idolatry</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Man created in, of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=27'>Gen 1:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=5&verse=1'>Gen 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=6'>Gen 9:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=3&verse=9'>Jas 3:9</a> <br/> - Regenerated into<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=17&verse=15'>Psa 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=29'>Rom 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=3&verse=18'>2Co 3:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=4&verse=24'>Eph 4:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=10'>Col 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=3'>1Jn 3:3</a> <br/> - Christ, of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=1&verse=15'>Col 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=1&verse=3'>Heb 1:3</a> <br/> - Of jealousy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=3'>Eze 8:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=5'>Eze 8:5</a><br/><a href='S:Idol'>Idol</a>; <a href='S:Idolatry'>Idolatry</a> "}]}